    </p>
    <p/>
    <p><b>Numerus</b></p>
    <p>Ideographic writings of numerical data should not be represented phonetically but designated
      through “.pl” and “.du”. For details see chapter <xref
        href="grammar_structure_convention.dita"/>.</p>
